<%- include('header'); -%>
<html>

  <body>
    <header>
      <h1>Lifestyle Newsletter</h1>
      <p>Stay updated with the latest tips and trends for a better life!</p>
    </header>
    <main>
      <h2>Health & Wellness</h2>
      <p>Looking for the latest tips and trends to help you live your best life? Look no further than the Lifestyle Newsletter! Our experts bring you the latest news and insights on health and wellness, food and recipes, travel and adventure, and entertainment and culture.</p>
      <p>Want to stay healthy and happy? Our Health & Wellness section has got you covered with tips for exercise, diet, and mindfulness, as well as the latest wellness trends to help you live your best life.</p>
      <h2>Food & Recipes</h2>
      <p>Looking for some delicious new recipes to try? Our Food & Recipes section is your go-to source for the latest trends in food and drink, as well as mouth-watering recipes to delight your taste buds.</p>
      <h2>Travel & Adventure</h2>
      <p>Ready for your next adventure? Our Travel & Adventure section takes you on a journey to explore new destinations and offers travel tips to help you plan your next great escape.</p>
      <h2>Entertainment & Culture</h2>
      <p>Finally, our Entertainment & Culture section keeps you up-to-date with the latest news and insights on music, film, television, art, and more, as well as exploring the rich diversity of cultures from around the world.</p>
      <h2>Sign up for our newsletter</h2>
      <form action="/" method="post">
        <input type="text" id="name" name="firstname" required autofocus placeholder="First Name" size="32">
        <br><br>
        <input type="text" name="lastname" value="" placeholder="Lastname" size="32">
        <br><br>
        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required placeholder="Email" size="32">
        <br><br>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Sign up</button>
      </form>
    </main>
    <footer>
      <p>&copy; 2023 Lifestyle Newsletter</p>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
